Package entity

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • entity.User
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Applicant, Manager
    public abstract class User
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract base class representing a user in the housing application system. This class provides the foundation for all user types in the system (Applicants, Officers, and Managers). It manages essential personal information like name, NRIC, age, and authentication credentials, as well as housing-related attributes like marital status and search preferences. All user types inherit these common attributes and behaviors while implementing their own specialized functionality.
